    img#brick(src='assets/images/brick.png', style='display:none;')
    img#border(src='assets/images/border.png', style='display:none;')
    #instructions_modal(style='display:none;')
        .instructions_modal__content
            span#instructions_modal__close &times;
            p.instructions_modal__text
                | <span class="instructions_modal__heading">Controls:</span> Use the arrow keys or A, W, S, and D to control the tank. Shoot with space bar. On mobile device use the NES controller arrows and A button. <br/>
            p.instructions_modal__text
                | <span class="instructions_modal__heading">SINGLE PLAYER mode:</span>  The objective is to destroy all 20 enemy tanks while protecting the eagle.<br/>
            p.instructions_modal__text
                | <span class="instructions_modal__heading">In MULTIPLAYER mode:</span> The objective is to destroy other tanks while remaining alive as long as possible.
                | Notice on the right panel under your username there is the score and lives count. <br/>

